              </td>
              <td>
                <p><a href="https://www.parliament.scot/chamber-and-committees/committees/current-and-previous-committees/session-6-delegated-powers-and-law-reform-committee/meetings/2024/delegated-powers-and-law-reform-committee-26-march-2024/minutes"><u>Minutes of proceedings</u></a></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Evidence session (16 April 2024)</p>
